description:
CRITICAL: Timer not cleaned up on successful tool execution.

**Location:** `packages/ai-functions/src/tool-orchestration.ts:453-459`

**Problem:**
```typescript
if (toolTimeout) {
  const timeoutPromise = new Promise<never>((_, reject) => {
    setTimeout(() => reject(new Error('Tool execution timeout')), toolTimeout)
  })
  result = await Promise.race([executePromise, timeoutPromise])
}
```

Timer continues running after tool completes, causing memory leaks.

**Fix:** Store timer ID and clear on completion.

