## 7. Error Handling Hooks

### 7.1 Global Error Handlers

```typescript
// In Workflow definition
const workflow = Workflow($ => {
  // Register handlers...
}, {
  onError: async (error, context) => {
    // Global error handling
    await alerting.notify(error)
  },
  onRetry: (attempt, error, context) => {
    metrics.increment('workflow.retry', { attempt })
  },
  onDLQ: (entry) => {
    logger.warn('Event sent to DLQ', entry)
  },
})
```

### 7.2 Per-Event Error Handlers

```typescript
$.on.Payment.process(
  async (payment, $) => {
    await processPayment(payment)
  },
  {
    onError: async (error, payment, $) => {
      // Event-specific error handling
      await notifyPaymentTeam(payment, error)
    },
  }
)
```

